Package: omicviz
Title: Visualization of HOMER Known Motif Discovery Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Huan Yang", email = "hyang333@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Parses and visualizes HOMER known motif discovery results and
    DESeq2 differential expression results. Provides an S4 class 'HomerData'
    to store parsed results and functions to create publication-quality
    ComplexHeatmap visualizations including motif rank, transcription factor
    names, motif logos, significance (-log P-value), and target percentage
    bar plots. Also provides volcano plot visualization for DESeq2 results.
